				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \beta = 0.82 $$\end{document}β=0.82. The overall temporal evolution of the total number of cases, i.e., all three phases, may also be interpreted by modeling. It is found that the duplication time \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
